		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<langdata>chi</langdata>
			<abstract>China Roads, 1990 is a line theme representing the roads in China, circa the late 1980s.  This dataset is based on DCW data (late 1980s), uncorrected.  Note:  China has greatly expanded roads since 1990.  Version 4:  reprojected to Gauss Kruger Xian 1980 Zone 19.</abstract>
			<purpose>Digital Chart of the World (ESRI / DMA datasets), processed for use with CHGIS data layers.</purpose>
